        "timestamp": "2017-08-29 21:55:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nMany of the debian files referenced in the pgaas setup files no longer exist in R1/Amsterdam.\nThis will certainly bring up a single-node postgres container, which is fine for some applications; I'm not sure if all of the capabilities exercised by the pgaas packages will translate well into a container, and would prefer working with the team trying this out.\nThe cluster name needs to be changed from \"pstg\" to something else to reduce confusion between clusters.\nThe R1/Amsterdam pgaas code also uses a different method for creating roles and databases than the R0/1702 code base.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
